llywood \n\t \n \n\t RE/ASIAN CUISINE \n\t \n\t\t RE/ASIAN CUISINE,  Bahrain \n\t \n \n \n RETAIL Catering Join Our Team Contact Us Wolfgangpuck.com respects our visitors and their privacy. You are free to visit parts of our site anonymously (without telling us who you are or revealing any information about yourself), but you may be required to register in order to view certain portions of our site or to take advantage of some special services. Our company will only use the information you provide us to deliver services you specifically request. We promise not to sell, rent, or share registered visitor\u2019s information with other people or unaffiliated companies except under the following circumstances: 1.  We respond to subpoenas, court orders, or legal process, or to establish or exercise our legal rights or defend against legal claims; 2.  We believe it is necessary to share information in order to investigate, prevent, or take action regarding illegal activities, suspected fraud, situations involving potential threats to the physical safety or any person, violations of Wolfgangpuck.com\u2019s terms of use, or as otherwise required by law; 3.  We transfer information about you if Wolfgangpuck.com and Wolfgang Puck Worldwide, Inc. is acquired by or merged with another company; 4.  You request or authorize it; 5.  The information is provided to help complete a transaction for you; or 6.  The information is provided to our agents, outside vendors or service providers to perform functions on our behalf such as analyzing data, providing marketing assistance, providing customer assistance, etc.. If you choose to register with Wolfgangpuck.com, we collect your name, address, telephone number, email address, interests you have in our products and services, or other information you give us voluntarily. With your permission, we automatically place your name on our email newsletter list so we can send you emails with information and special offers. You can update your information or preferences by resubmitting a registration form. Your personal information will be automatically updated every time you register with the same email address. Also, you can unsubscribe to our newsletters by clicking on the \u201cunsubscribe\u201d button at the bottom of a newsletter. We do not require you to provide any information which would identify you personally (\u201cPersonally Identifiable Information\u201d), although you may submit such information if you choose to register on our site. If you send us an inquiry or request by e-mail, we may retain your e-mail address after we respond to your request or inquiry. We may use this e-mail address to contact you in the future with product or service information which we believe may be of interest to you. We may gather usage information while you use the site and transfer the information to our servers as frequently as nightly. Our web servers track and collect the visitor\u2019s domain name and IP address, but not the email address. This information is aggregated to measure the number of visits, average time spent on the Site, pages viewed, and so on. We use this information (\u201cSite Usage Information\u201d) to measure the use of our site and to improve the content of our site. We may share with third parties such as marketing or service providers experiential information or other data which does not personally identify you or other users of our site. This might include product or service preferences of all visitors to our site, for example. If you choose to send information to us with respect to a career with our company or a franchise opportunity with our company we will retain such information and we (our employees and agents) will use it in connection with such a career or franchise opportunity. We may share such information with our affiliates but will not share it with third parties. Cookies are alphanumeric identifiers that are transferred to your computer from websites you visit. These identifiers are maintained on your computer\u2019s hard drive and store information about your and web browsing habits. Wolfgangpuck.com uses cookies to monitor our visitors viewing habits. These cookies may allow us and our service providers to customize your experience and make your visit to our website easier, measure activity on our website, track conversions, target ads, and provide analytics. While some cookies are deleted when you close your browser, others remain even after you close your browsing session. To manage your cookies, you can set your web browser to refuse cookies. For more information on how to manage browser cookies, click  here . You can also contact us by  clicking here  to update or correct certain personal information, or to opt out. To enhance your visit to our website, Wolfgangpuck.com has links to other sites on the internet that are owned and operated by third parties. Wolfgangpuck.com is not capable of controlling the cookies or privacy policies of other websites; therefore it is not responsible for the actions of the websites that link to or from our site. Neither Wolfgangpuck.com nor Wolfgang Puck Worldwide, Inc. own or operate any website other than Wolfgangpuck.com. We do not knowingly attempt to solicit or receive any information from children. Our terms and conditions of use require that any registration may only be made by those over the age of 18 and that any product or service purchases may only be made by those over the age of 18. By using our services, you are representing that you are an adult (at least 18 years of age) or have the permission from a parent or legal guardian to use our service. If we have reason to believe that information is being provided by a child under the age of 18, the Company will not collect the information without parental consent or parent notification, which will include the opportunity for the parent to prevent the use of the information or to prevent the child\u2019s participation in the activity. Without parental consent, online information will only be used to respond to an unsolicited request and for no other purposes. We recognize that protecting children\u2019s identities and privacy online is important and that the responsibility to do so rests with both the online industry and with parents. We maintain numerous security standards and procedures to help prevent unauthorized access to confidential information about you. Our Site uses encryption technology, digital certificates, secure commerce servers and authentication to protect your Personally Identifiable Information. As long as the web browser you are using supports Secure Sockets Layer (SSL), your information will be submitted to us with a high level of security. We update and test our security technology on an ongoing basis. While we take reasonable measures to prevent the loss or misuse of the information that you provide to us, including but not limited to, your Personally Identifiable Information, due to factors beyond our control, we do not guarantee that your Personally Identifiable Information or any other information collected by us will be completely secure from misappropriation by hackers or other third parties or from other criminal activities. Wolfgangpuck.com will occasionally send our registered guest information to third-party subcontractors that work on our behalf to provide certain services. Examples include sending postal mailings and emails, removing repetitive information from our databases, analyzing data, and providing marketing assistance. These third parties do not have the right to use or distribute your personal information beyond what is necessary to assist us. They are contractually obligated to maintain confidentiality and security of your personal information and are restricted from using this information in any way not expressly authorized by Wolfgangpuck.com. This policy was last modified on March 19, 2003. Wolfgangpuck.com reserves the right to modify or amend this policy at any time by posting the revised policy on our site. The policy will always be available on our website for visitors and registered guests to view. If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, or if you believe that we have not adhered to this Privacy Policy, please contact us via email or write to: Wolfgang Puck Worldwide, Inc. \nAttn: Website Privacy Policy \n8687 Melrose Ave. \nRoom B315, Blue Building \nWest Hollywood, CA 90069 310.432.1500 We welcome your questions and comments. \u201cWolfgang Puck\u201d\u00ae is a trademark of Wolfgang Puck Worldwide, Inc. All other trademarks are the property of their respective owners. * \u0394 document.getElementById( \"ak_js_1\" ).setAttribute( \"value\", ( new Date() ).getTime() ); \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t  youtube \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t facebook \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \t\t\t\t instagram Locations Products Contact Us Gift Cards Terms & Conditions Privacy Policy Wolfgang Puck \u00a9 2023", "size": 121123, "depth": 1, "download_timeout": 180.0, "download_slot": "wolfgangpuck.com", "download_latency": 0.22481083869934082, "status": 200, "links_url": "https://wolfgangpuck.com/about-us/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/restaurants/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/restaurants/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/privacy-policy/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/spago/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/restaurants/spago-beverly-hills/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/restaurants/spago-budapest/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/restaurants/spago-istanbul/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/restaurants/spago-las-vegas/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/restaurants/spago-maui/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/restaurants/spago-saudi-arabia/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/restaurants/spago-singapore/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/privacy-policy/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/privacy-policy/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/cut/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/restaurants/cut-bahrain/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/restaurants/cut-bever