the best of Wolfgang\u2019s signature dishes with Mediterranean influences, innovative takes on comfort food classics, and handcrafted specialty cocktails, beer, and wine. SELECT YOUR LOCATION LAS VEGAS \n ORLANDO Main Street, Santa Monica.  Since opening in 1983, Chinois on Main has boldly combined Chinese tradition and fresh California ingredients with contemporary French techniques and introduced the world to Asian fusion cuisine. LEARN MORE \n MAKE A RESERVATION Pendry West Hollywood Hotel, Rooftop.  Merois celebrates the open-air allure of the City of Angels with a menu that spotlights Chef Wolfgang Puck\u2019s eye for the sophisticated subtleties of Japanese, Southeast Asian and French/California cuisine. LEARN MORE \n MAKE A RESERVATION Pendry West Hollywood Hotel, Street Level.  The casual European style caf\u00e9 features a relaxed, all-day menu of neighborhood-friendly favorites including classic salads, handmade pastas, vegan dishes and renowned Wolfgang Puck house-made pizzas, fresh from Ospero\u2019s wood-burning pizza oven. LEARN MORE \n MAKE A RESERVATION Featuring Wolfgang\u2019s signature modern approach to traditional Asian cuisine, the restaurant offers a \u201cre\u201d-evolution of the contemporary and classic cooking styles, techniques and flavors of China, Japan, Thailand, Vietnam, and other far eastern destinations. LEARN MORE \n MAKE A RESERVATION Wolfgang Puck Catering sets the standard for culinary excellence, bringing Wolfgang\u2019s legendary combination of innovative cuisine and refined service to the worlds\u2019 most renowned and demanding corporate, cultural and entertainment clients. Our team brings authentic ingredients, culinary expertise and a restaurant-quality experience to your special events in a celebration of good company and good food. Whether you\u2019re hosting an intimate gathering, a black-tie fundraising gala or a casual birthday barbecue, the Wolfgang Puck Catering team delivers Chef Wolfgang\u2019s legendary passion 