 \n\t \n\t\t CHINOIS,  Santa Monica \n\t \n \n\t MEROIS \n\t \n\t\t MEROIS,  West Hollywood \n\t \n \n\t OSPERO \n\t \n\t\t OSPERO,  West Hollywood \n\t \n \n\t RE/ASIAN CUISINE \n\t \n\t\t RE/ASIAN CUISINE,  Bahrain \n\t \n \n \n RETAIL Catering Join Our Team Contact Us Brian Becher  Executive Chef |  Fabio Marques  Restaurant Director Located at the Four Seasons Bahrain Bay, guests enter the acclaimed restaurant through a dramatic staircase from the bar and lounge below. The sleek and modern American steak restaurant delivers innovation at every level through its unique culinary, service and design combination. The menu features the widest and best selection of beef available, along with premium shellfish and whole fresh fish. Guests are treated to a view of the chef\u2019s state-of-the-art kitchen and a striking panorama that extends over the pool and across the hotel\u2019s lush grounds to the city of Manama. CUT, BAHRAIN \n The Four Seasons Bahrain Bay \nBahrain, 334, Bahrain \nManama, Bahrain Reservations are recommended Lunch \nSaturday \u2013 Thursday: 12:30PM \u2013 3PM \nClosed Friday Brunch \nFriday 12:30PM \u2013 3PM Dinner \nSaturday \u2013 Tuesday 7PM \u2013 11PM \nWednesday \u2013 Friday 7PM \u2013 11PM CUT Lounge \nSaturday \u2013 Tuesday 12:30PM \u2013 1AM \nWednesday \u2013 Friday 12:30PM \u2013 2AM Make A Reservation CALL +973 1711 5044 GET Directions CUT is available for private dining, gatherings, group dinners and corporate events. Please contact us by phone for more information.  +973 1711 5044  /  32300171 . The CUT kitchen dining experience conveys Wolfgang Puck hospitality in its most immersive form. Guests embark on a menu-free bespoke and interactive culinary journey at the kitchen counter and away from the typical setting of a restaurant dining room table. We offer a 5 course menu for 70 BHD 5 Course with Non-Al Pairing and 110 BHD 5 Course with Alcohol Pairing The experience is available Tuesday \u2013 Friday during dinner service, maxi