CK BAR & GRILL \n\t \n\t\t WOLFGANG PUCK BAR & GRILL,  Las Vegas \n\t\t WOLFGANG PUCK BAR & GRILL,  Orlando \n\t \n \n\t CHINOIS \n\t \n\t\t CHINOIS,  Santa Monica \n\t \n \n\t MEROIS \n\t \n\t\t MEROIS,  West Hollywood \n\t \n \n\t OSPERO \n\t \n\t\t OSPERO,  West Hollywood \n\t \n \n\t RE/ASIAN CUISINE \n\t \n\t\t RE/ASIAN CUISINE,  Bahrain \n\t \n \n \n RETAIL Catering Join Our Team Contact Us Drew Rosenberg  Executive Chef |  Charles Hueston  General Manager As the original location of CUT, this Wolfgang Puck Fine Dining restaurant consistently ranks as one of the most sought-after steak restaurants in the world. CUT was awarded a coveted star by MICHELIN Guide in 2019 and again in 2021, securing the restaurant among the ranks of the finest in all of California. Offering a contemporary twist on the classic steakhouse, the menu highlights various cuts of the finest beef from regions across the globe, as well as shellfish, seafood and an extensive international wine list. Located in the Beverly Wilshire Hotel you will experience the best of culinary, modern architecture, art, and 5-star hospitality. CUT, BEVERLY HILLS \nBeverly Wilshire,  A Four Seasons Hotel \n 9500 Wilshire Blvd. \nBeverly Hills, CA, USA 90212 Reservations are recommended \nValet parking available CUT \nClosed Sunday \u2013 Monday \nTuesday \u2013 Thursday 5:30PM \u2013 10PM \nFriday \u2013 Saturday 5PM \u2013 10:30PM CUT Lounge \nClosed Sunday \u2013 Monday \nTuesday \u2013 Thursday 5:30PM \u2013 10PM \nFriday \u2013 Saturday 5PM \u2013 11:00PM Make A Reservation CALL (310) 276-8500 GET Directions CUT by Wolfgang Puck at Beverly Wilshire, A Four Seasons Hotel is the perfect place to celebrate a special occasion. Our private and semi-private dining spaces, a full restaurant buyout, or the intimate CUT Lounge provide the perfect setting for any sized special occasion. This Wolfgang Puck renowned restaurant at this legendary Hollywood landmark, promises to deliver extraordinary cuisine and impeccable service to create a most memorable experience. VIEW MENU \u00a0 CAPACITIES: \n Petit CUT (Private Dining Room):  up to 24 seated; 30 reception \n Rodeo Dr. Tier (semi-private):  up to 25 seated \n Entire Restaurant:  up to 160 seated; 300 reception \n CUT Lounge:  up to 60 seated; 100 reception For further information or to reserve your next group event, please email  cutevents.beverlywilshire@fourseasons.com  or call  (310) 275-5200 . @CUTBEVERLYHILLS \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \t\t\t\t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t * \u0394 document.getElementById( \"ak_js_1\" ).setAttribute( \"value\", ( new Date() ).getTime() ); \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t  youtube \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t facebook \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \t\t\t\t instagram Locations Products Contact Us Gift Cards Terms & Conditions Privacy Policy Wolfgang Puck \u00a9 2023", "size": 129383, "depth": 1, "download_timeout": 180.0, "download_slot": "wolfgangpuck.com", "download_latency": 2.1622400283813477, "status": 200, "links_url": "https://wolfgangpuck.com/about-us/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/restaurants/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/restaurants/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/restaurants/cut-beverly-hills/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/spago/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/restaurants/spago-beverly-hills/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/restaurants/spago-budapest/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/restaurants/spago-istanbul/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/restaurants/spago-las-vegas/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/restaurants/spago-maui/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/restaurants/spago-saudi-arabia/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/restaurants/spago-singapore/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/restaurants/cut-beverly-hills/@@https://wolfgangpuck.com/restaurants/cut-beverly-h