n\t CHINOIS \n\t \n\t\t CHINOIS,  Santa Monica \n\t \n \n\t MEROIS \n\t \n\t\t MEROIS,  West Hollywood \n\t \n \n\t OSPERO \n\t \n\t\t OSPERO,  West Hollywood \n\t \n \n\t RE/ASIAN CUISINE \n\t \n\t\t RE/ASIAN CUISINE,  Bahrain \n\t \n \n \n RETAIL Catering Join Our Team Contact Us Daniel No  Executive Chef |  Kassey Wolf  General Manager Located within the Four Seasons Resort Maui at Wailea, Spago\u2019s Hawaiian outpost embraces the tradition of the islands\u2019 culinary techniques and offers many locally-inspired dishes along with Wolfgang\u2019s classics. Pair your meal with a selection from the international wine collection or try a refreshing interpretation of a classic Hawaiian libation from the specialty cocktail menu. Casually elegant the dining room and intimate lounge set the stage for spectacular ocean views and the most spectacular sunsets from the Lanai. SPAGO, MAUI \nFour Seasons Resort Maui at Wailea \n 3900 Wailea Alanui \nMaui, HI, USA 96753 Reservations are recommended \nValet parking available DINNER \nNightly, 5PM \u2013 8:30PM LOUNGE \nOpens nightly at 5PM Make A Reservation CALL (808) 879-2999 GET Directions UPCOMING EVENTS Be a guest at your own event when you celebrate at Spago, located within the Four Seasons Resort Maui at Wailea. This one-of-a-kind venue can host groups both large and small on the Lanai or point of the Lanai spaces, or in the full restaurant for a complete buy-out. Whether you are celebrating a company gathering or birthday festivities, our talented staff and world-renowned cuisine will help create an unforgettable affair. For further information or to reserve your next group event, please contact our catering department at  maui.events@wolfgangpuck.com . \n @SPAGOMAUI \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \t\t\t\t \t\t\t\t\t\t\