n \n\t WOLFGANG PUCK BAR & GRILL \n\t \n\t\t WOLFGANG PUCK BAR & GRILL,  Las Vegas \n\t\t WOLFGANG PUCK BAR & GRILL,  Orlando \n\t \n \n\t CHINOIS \n\t \n\t\t CHINOIS,  Santa Monica \n\t \n \n\t MEROIS \n\t \n\t\t MEROIS,  West Hollywood \n\t \n \n\t OSPERO \n\t \n\t\t OSPERO,  West Hollywood \n\t \n \n\t RE/ASIAN CUISINE \n\t \n\t\t RE/ASIAN CUISINE,  Bahrain \n\t \n \n \n RETAIL Catering Join Our Team Contact Us Matt Broeze  Executive Chef |  Roberto Garcia  General Manager See and be seen at Las Vegas\u2019 most popular dining destination, Spago, located within The Bellagio Hotel. This one-of-a-kind venue with spectacular front row fountain entertainment can host groups both large and small in the banquet and private dining spaces, or main dining room. No matter the occasion, our talented staff will help to create a memorable experience with impeccable service, unmatched hospitality and the celebrity chef\u2019s world famous cuisine. SPAGO, LAS VEGAS \nBellagio Hotel & Casino \n 3600 Las Vegas Blvd S \nLas Vegas, NV, USA 89109 Reservations are recommended Brunch \nFriday \u2013 Sunday 11AM \u2013 2:30PM Dinner \nMonday \u2013 Sunday 5PM \u2013 10PM Make A Reservation CALL (702) 693-8181 GET Directions UPCOMING EVENTS Spago Las Vegas at the Bellagio Hotel is beautifully situated for al fresco dining in front of the famous Bellagio Fountains. The menu features Puck\u2019s signature California fare paired with inspiration from his chef\u2019s weekly trips to the farmer\u2019s market. Menus feature handmade pastas, wood-oven pizzas, fresh seafood, all-natural meats and prime steaks, alongside handcrafted cocktails and a robust wine list. To complete the meal, dessert complements the menu with an array of seasonal delights sure to make your experience memorable. CAPACITIES \nSEATING CAPACITY Two Private Dining Rooms:  20 Guests Each Patio:  50 Guests Buyout:  120 Guests STANDING CAPACITY Patio:  75-100 Guests Buyout:  250 Guests For further information or to reserve y