abia \n\t\t SPAGO,  Singapore \n\t \n \n\t CUT \n\t \n\t\t CUT,  Bahrain \n\t\t CUT,  Beverly Hills \n\t\t CUT,  Las Vegas \n\t\t CUT,  London \n\t\t CUT,  New York \n\t\t CUT,  Singapore \n\t\t CUT,  Washington D.C. \n\t \n \n\t WOLFGANG PUCK BAR & GRILL \n\t \n\t\t WOLFGANG PUCK BAR & GRILL,  Las Vegas \n\t\t WOLFGANG PUCK BAR & GRILL,  Orlando \n\t \n \n\t CHINOIS \n\t \n\t\t CHINOIS,  Santa Monica \n\t \n \n\t MEROIS \n\t \n\t\t MEROIS,  West Hollywood \n\t \n \n\t OSPERO \n\t \n\t\t OSPERO,  West Hollywood \n\t \n \n\t RE/ASIAN CUISINE \n\t \n\t\t RE/ASIAN CUISINE,  Bahrain \n\t \n \n \n RETAIL Catering Join Our Team Contact Us Ari Rosenson  Executive Chef |  Steve Scott Springer  General Manager |  Areg Avanessian  Chef de Cuisine Located in the heart of Beverly Hills along Canon Drive, Spago is the flagship restaurant of the Wolfgang Puck Fine Dining Group. The sleek and simple design of the restaurant enhances the iconic, market-driven menus and exceptional level of service for which the restaurant is best known. Guests can choose from a seasonal a la carte menu, or explore the best of the west with the chefs\u2019 multi-course California Tasting Menu. SPAGO, BEVERLY HILLS \n 176 North Canon Drive \nBeverly Hills, CA, USA 90210 Reservations are recommended \nValet parking available Closed Monday \nTuesday \u2013 Thursday 5PM \u2013 10PM \nFriday \u2013 Saturday 5PM \u2013 10:30PM \nSunday 5PM \u2013 10PM Make A Reservation CALL (310) 385-0880 GET Directions UPCOMING EVENTS No matter the occasion or time of day, our expert events team, coupled with our world-renowned cuisine and hospitality, will guarantee a most memorable event. With the capability of hosting both on and off-premise events we look forward to serving you and your guests. VIEW EVENT BROCHURE CAPACITIES Private Dining Room 1:  15 to 24 seated; 35 reception Private Dining Room 2:  25 to 60 seated; 100 reception Private Dining Room 1 & 2:  88 seated; 175 reception Gallery (semi-private):  36 seated; 50 reception Private Dining Room 1, 2 & Gallery:  150 seated; 250 reception \nEntire Restaurant: 300 seated, 550 reception For further information or to reserve your next group event, please submit an inquiry below, or contact our catering department directly at  310.777.3711 \n Private Event Software powered by Tripleseat If you are traveling East on Wilshire Blvd. make a left on Beverly Dr., then make a right on Dayton Way. Travel one block East until you reach Canon Dr. and make a right onto Canon Dr. Make a U-turn at the bottom of Canon Dr. at the closure in order to access the Spago Beverly Hills valet. If you are traveling west on Wilshire Blvd. make a right on N. Redford Dr., then a left onto Brighton Way. Continue going west on Brighton Way until you reach Canon Dr. Make a left turn on Canon Dr. and continue south on Canon Dr. until you reach the subway closure. Make a U-turn at the end of Canon Dr. in order to access the Spago Beverly Hills valet. Closure General Information: The intensity of the construction and police presence will lessen over the course of the next few weeks. The closure at the corner of Canon Dr. and Wilshire Blvd. will remain up for approximately the next two years, as we await the exciting completion of the Metro Purple Line Station at the corner of Wilshire and Canon. \nThe closure allows for legal U-turns at the base of Canon Dr. allowing guests much easier access to Spago Beverly Hills. VIEW EVENTS @SPAGOBH \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \t\t\t\t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t * \u0394 document.getElementById( \"ak_js_1\" ).setAttribute( \"value\", ( new Date() ).getTime() ); \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t  youtube \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t facebook \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t